item.title: Mingshuai Liu
item.description: Biography Mingshuai Liu received the B.S. degree in Information Science and Technology from Hebei University of Science and Technology, China, in 2018. He is currently working toward a master’s degree in computer technology at University of Science and Technology Beijing (USTB). Publication [1] M. Liu, W. Zheng, C. Huang, L. Wang, S. Li, Y. Wu, Y. Zhong, and L. Zhang, “Soil Moisture Time Series Forecasting with GPR Model and Radially Uniform Design,” IEEE Access, under revision.
